snippet.title: BeatBeat  - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Join the BeatBeat discord!: https://discord.gg/RU9FAWy 

Steam store page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1225840/BeatBeat/

BeatBeat is a rhythm platformer with vaporwave aesthetics and future-funky beats. Groove your way through arcade-style levels that bring home the feel of those big arcades you always see in the movies.

Website: https://beatbeatgame.com
